<br>
One suggestion I can give to all of you, is that the biles should be collected first and you should bring the bile extractor and the coldain tanning kit with you while you are collecting as nothing in this part stacks.  Currently I have 2 glowing silks, 3 biles, 2 fibers, and 4 threads which will be 3 glowing silks and 2 biles oncxe I get one more thread, so it really does save space and is pretty much necassary unless you vacate all your inventory slots.<br>
<br>
